events.name: Coastal Carolina Chanticleers at James Madison Dukes

headlines.description: Alonza Barnett III sandwiched a touchdown pass and a touchdown run around a pick-6 by Lloyd Summerall III in a big second quarter and James Madison breezed to a 39-7 victory over Coastal Carolina on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Alonza Barnett III, Lloyd Summerall III spark James Madison to 39-7 romp over Coastal Carolina

events.name: Middle Tennessee Blue Raiders at Louisiana Tech Bulldogs

headlines.description: Freshman Evan Bullock threw touchdown passes on four straight drives to open the game and ran for a score on the fifth as Louisiana Tech cruised to a 48-21 victory over Middle Tennessee on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Freshman Evan Bullock has 5 TD passes, rushing score as Louisiana Tech thumps Middle Tennessee 48-21

events.name: UTEP Miners at Western Kentucky Hilltoppers

headlines.description: Caden Veltkamp threw three touchdown passes and ran for a score, Michael Mathison had two touchdown catches and a touchdown run, and Western Kentucky cruised to a 44-17 victory over winless UTEP on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Caden Veltkamp, Michael Mathison guide Western Kentucky to 44-17 victory over winless UTEP

headlines.description: Kenny Dillingham screamed through an adrenaline-fueled interview and got caught up in a student mosh pit.
headlines.shortLinkText: Cam Skattebo runs for 156 yards and 2 TDs, Arizona State knocks off No. 16 Utah 27-19

events.name: Northwestern Wildcats at Maryland Terrapins

headlines.description: Defensive end Aidan Hubbard returned a fumble recovery for a touchdown in the fourth quarter, and Northwestern pulled away from Maryland 37-10 on Friday night for its first Big Ten victory this season.
headlines.shortLinkText: Northwestern exploits Maryland's turnovers, rolls 37-10 to earn first Big Ten victory

events.name: UNLV Rebels at Utah State Aggies

headlines.description: Hajj-Malik Williams threw three first-half touchdown passes, Kylin James ran for three TDs and UNLV erupted for 27 second-quarter points Friday night as the Runnin' Rebels beat Utah State 50-34.
headlines.shortLinkText: Williams throws 3 TD passes; UNLV scores 27 2nd-quarter points, beats Utah State 50-34
